cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with semantic segmentation of images, which is a topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of stylized data and adaptation techniques also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG). The uncertainty-aware evaluation framework and metric could also fall under graphics (cs.GR) or multimedia (cs.MM) categories.
